Shivya pathania shares the experience of her beautiful journey across leh, Ladakh and her experience with the students of druk padma karpo school as they were mesmerized by her and the products of Uniball. She has always been an avid writer and loved the idea of making people aware about the importance of writing in their lives. She also tells us that we shouldn’t be too dependent on technology as it can fail anytime but your pen and paper will always be there with you in any part of the world.

#Anighttoremember...It’s a long Read...
God Saved Us...
.
17400 ft #Changlapass 
Avalanche area
10:30 pm IST
No Network No Help
Cars Skidding!!
.
Woh Kehte hai na till the time it happens to you.. one will never understand.. A night we can never forget, The last day of our shoot.. While coming back we got stuck and how.. At one point of time all I was scared was to not being able to say the last Goodbye.. The I loved you for lifetime, you were important to me...to my loved ones.. Life is really short to have grudges or to hate or to even not like someone..You never know what’s gonna happen the next moment.. At that time all I could think was these were not just quotes on life.. IT IS THE REALITY..We loose humanity on the way in our busy lives,in the bhed chal that we forget to actually LIVE EACH SECOND.. 
I wish I could pen down what I really felt that night.. I am numb I am scared but how I am thank full to God because it was only GOD who saved us💕❤️
To this new life..

latestIgtvVideos.title: @the_house_of_artisans
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Can you donate one cup of coffee today?
That’s all it takes for a family of four to have survive for 1 day!

They all can have 3 meals a day for just 140 rupees!

From the time COVID hit us, their work has been affected severely!
They are so desperate to survive that they are giving their daughters in exchange for 4200 rupees/month!
We cannot let this happen!
That’s why I am supporting @the_house_of_artisans , who are saving 200 artisan families from a lifelong debt!
All they need is 140 rupees a day for 1 family!
Swipe up to my story to do your bit! 
The Link is also in the bio.
Let’s change their lives together!
@bpraak  @balanvidya

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
.
Yes I felt alone..coz I din go home where my #family is  but when I looked around I saw @tanyakaur_ @fatehrandhawaa who cannot go to their respective countries too..They are my family here in #mumbai and what I am doing is for my family's safety  too..my father said "Duties are bigger and more important than our emotions"
Its our duty to take care of one and all.
The least we can do is STAY HOME STAY SAFE...KEEP EVERYONE SAFE!!
.
*WASH YOUR HANDS EVERY 20 MINUTES PROPERLY..
.
*DO YOUR HOUSE CHORES YOURSELF, CLEAN THE AREAS AGAIN AND SANITIZE THEM PROPERLY..
.
*YOU ARE WITH YOUR PEOPLE ALREADY ,SPEND QUALITY TIME WITH THEM.."YOU ARE LUCKY" TRUST ME...
.
*LEARN NEW THINGS,READ AND YA COME UP WITH INTERESTING THINGS.
.
*HELP HELP THE PEOPLE WORKING FOR YOU..THEY NEED YOU NOW..DONT CUT THEIR PAYMENTS..EDUCATE THEM ON CALL..
.

FUN FACT @tanyakaur_  is coming up with legit choreo and @fatehrandhawaa  is gona let me know some new food techniques..❤️
